<Base title="SocialProof for Attorneys & Law Firms — Client Testimonials That Win Clients | SocialProof" description="Attorneys: build the trust that converts consultations into retained clients. SocialProof helps law firms collect and display client testimonials compliantly and effectively.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Attorneys & Law Firms
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        When someone needs a lawyer, they're often scared. They're facing their biggest problem — a divorce, a DUI, a business dispute, an injury. They need to know you've helped people in exactly their situation. SocialProof helps law firms collect and display compelling client testimonials that turn anxious searchers into booked consultations.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why testimonials matter in legal services</h2>
      <p>People searching for an attorney are overwhelmed and uncertain. They don't understand legalese. They can't evaluate your credentials. What they CAN evaluate is whether other people in similar situations felt heard, helped, and well-served by you. Testimonials bridge the credibility gap that bar exam results and firm bio pages never can.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">The challenge: most attorneys don't have a system for collecting testimonials at the right moment — typically right after a favorable outcome when clients are most grateful. SocialProof makes it easy to capture that window.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What effective legal testimonials look like</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Outcome-focused:</strong> "She got my DUI reduced to reckless driving. I kept my job and my license."</li>
        <li><strong>Human connection:</strong> "He explained everything in plain English. I never felt lost or talked down to."</li>
        <li><strong>Responsiveness:</strong> "She returned calls the same day. I never had to wonder where my case stood."</li>
        <li><strong>Relief:</strong> "I was terrified walking in. I left feeling like someone was finally in my corner."</li>
        <li><strong>Practice-specific:</strong> "We mediated a fair custody agreement. My kids' lives stayed stable through it all."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for law firms</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Add the widget</strong> to practice area pages and your homepage — no technical setup required.</li>
        <li><strong>After a favorable outcome</strong>, send clients your SocialProof link when they're most appreciative.</li>
        <li><strong>Clients share voluntarily</strong> — no login, no forms, just a simple text box.</li>
        <li><strong>You review every submission</strong> before it goes live — full control over what's displayed.</li>
        <li><strong>Segment by practice area</strong> — show family law testimonials on your family law page, criminal defense on that page, etc.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for all practice areas</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Family law & divorce</li>
        <li>Personal injury & auto accidents</li>
        <li>Criminal defense</li>
        <li>Estate planning & probate</li>
        <li>Business & contract law</li>
        <li>Immigration & visa services</li>
        <li>Real estate law</li>
        <li>Employment & labor law</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background:#fdf4ff;border:1px solid #e9d5ff;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#6b21a8;">
          "I added SocialProof to my personal injury page and started sending the link after settlements. The testimonials I collected are specific — 'she got me $47,000 more than the insurance company offered.' That kind of social proof converts far better than any ad I've run."
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#581c87;">— Personal injury attorney, Southeast US</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Start free</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for 1 active widget. Start with your highest-traffic practice area page and watch consultation requests increase.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <a href="/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.85rem 2.2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
          Start collecting testimonials free
        </a>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#888;">Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
      </div>
